data.description: IMPROVED PRICE!!!     Escape to your own slice of paradise in the coveted eastlake shores community. This serene oasis offers the perfect blend of resort-style living and modern convenience, access to not one but two inviting pools, Featuring 3 bedrooms 2 bathrooms spacious and thoughtfully designed for optimal comfort, open concept living spaces ideal for entertaining or simply unwinding style, well appointed kitchen with modern appliances and ample storage space, access to exclusive amenities, showcasing a tranquil lake with an exclusive beach club. Enjoy leisurely strolls along the lake's edge, watching birds, ducks, and soaking sunrise views. Don't miss the opportunity to experience upscale living at it's finest.
